# Storefront design system

When editing customer-facing pages or storefront components, follow [docs/DESIGN.md](../../docs/DESIGN.md).

## Rules

- Use storefront tokens and components under `resources/js/components/storefront/`.
- Do **not** import admin components into storefront pages.
- Admin UI has its own system: [DESIGN_ADMIN.md](../../docs/DESIGN_ADMIN.md).

Preview catalog: `/preview/design-system`.
